Package: HMP
Type: Package
Title: Hypothesis Testing and Power Calculations for Comparing Metagenomic Samples from HMP
Version: 1.5
Date: 2017-06-12
Author: Patricio S. La Rosa, Elena Deych, Sharina Carter, Berkley Shands, William D. Shannon
